It‚Äôs quite possible that merchants will begin to follow suit as Bitcoin Cash continues to grow. However, as of now, Bitcoin Cash isn‚Äôt accepted by the absolute majority of vendors, even those that¬†<a href="https://cointelegraph.com/bitcoin-for-beginners/what-can-i-buy-with-bitcoins#video-games" target="_blank" rel="noopener">do accept the original Bitcoin</a>.

Thus, currently, the main use of Bitcoin Cash is investment.
